		<title>Questions for Steven Zacharius</title>
		<link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/ThePassiveVoice/~3/OPmmj1afmwQ/</link>
		<comments>http://www.thepassivevoice.com/12/2014/five-digital-publishing-questions-for-steven-zacharius/#comments</comments>
